Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Stagnant economy warning
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040byhs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Aug 1979
US Congress warns of economic stagnation as productivity declines. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.